<section class="pt-5 pb-3 bg-white text-center" id="what_is_omnilint">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="h1-responsive">What is Lint.dev</h1>
    <!-- <p class="lead mx-auto">Not every rule has the same importance. <br /> -->
    <!-- <p class="lead mx-auto mt-4 mb-4" style="max-width: 580px;">For every programming language, Lint.dev contains a glossary of rules, the recommanded best practices for each, and lets teams decide on what rule they enforce and with what severity level.</p> -->
    <p class="lead mx-auto mt-4 mb-4" style="max-width: 580px;">Lint.dev allows development teams to enforce, monitor and improve code quality within their teams.</p>


    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <!-- <img src="/images/features/tags.png" alt="ERBLint" height="100" width="100" class="mb-3"> -->
        <span class="fa fa-check-circle mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Analyze your commits</h4>
        <p>Lint.dev checks your code for every staged file you commit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <span class="fa fa-bolt mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Detect issues immediately</h4>
        <p>Get notified early in the development process, don't wait for your build to crash.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <span class="fa fa-shield mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Enforce code policies</h4>
        <p>Lint.dev allows team managers to install and maintained consistent rules.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <span class="fa fa-warning mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Get warnings</h4>
        <p>Receive warnings when your code contains an offense to a rule.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <span class="fa fa-dashboard mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Dashboard & charts</h4>
        <p>Get access to a full dashboard containing all the data you need in one place.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4 mb-4">
        <span class="fa fa-code mb-4" style="font-size: 70px;"></span>
        <h4>Multi-languages</h4>
        <p>Lint.dev currently works for HTML, CSS, Javascript, Ruby & Python.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>




